{"url": "https://www.her.ie/beauty/product-ariana-grande-uses-create-ponytail-surprising-362003", "text": "The product Ariana Grande uses to create her ponytail is surprising\n\nThe secret is out!\n\nQueen of pop Ariana Grande is known for rocking the slickest ponytail ever, so when her hairstylist spilled the details on the exact product he uses to create the rock solid do', we could not believe it.\n\nStylist to the stars Chris Appleton, who is renowned for creating all of Grande's hairstyles as well as looks for Kim Kardashian, Jennifer Lopez and Katy Perry, revealed the key product to E!'s Freestyle.\n\n\"It's called Gorilla Snot. It's a gel. Say I wanted to do a ponytail and I wanted to do something really slick, I'd just put that on the edges. It makes it like rock solid.\" He explained while conducting a hair demonstration for the entertainment channel.\n\nGorilla Snot is a sticky yellow hair gel, known as the \"best kept secret\" for steamrolling flyaways and keeping braids tight.\n\nAnd with a bit of rooting, we have found the product and surprisingly it's only \u20ac2.12. Celebrity hair for \u20ac2? YES PLEASE.\n\n\"If you want to make sure that ponytail is super sleek use a tiny little drop of it\" Appleton added as his top tip for recreating the singers look.\n\nThe product is available on Target here and ships to Ireland for \u20ac12.86.", "images": ["https://www.her.ie/assets/images/her/main-logo.svg?id=5d83db2642088bed19e5", "https://m0.her.ie/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/29141143/gorilla-gel.jpg", "https://img.maximummedia.ie/her_-image.png?id=d48286e7deecfc23eec6", "https://img.maximummedia.ie/her_-1024x681.jpg", "https://m0.her.ie/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/29142245/pony.jpg"], "top_img": "https://img.maximummedia.ie/her_-1024x681.jpg", "keywords": [], "authors": ["Denise Curtin"], "canonical_link": "https://www.her.ie/beauty/product-ariana-grande-uses-create-ponytail-surprising-362003", "title": "The product Ariana Grande uses to create her ponytail